"Show line numbers
set number

"Indentation (2 spaces for shift and tab)
set shiftwidth=2
set expandtab
set tabstop=2

"Auto indentation
set autoindent
set smartindent

"Disable word wrapping
set nowrap

"Appearance
"- force vim to use 256 colors
set t_Co=256

"- dark background
set background=dark

"- color scheme
colorscheme delek
